{"tid":1099542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[阿蝶夫人] 青衣持枴杖老婦失控 擸菜刀狂劈滙豐櫃員機被捕","createTime":"2019-04-10T00:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T08:23:09.000Z","uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a05cab1677bee82f989a253124dfbf99b430ba43","tid":1099542,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"【18:45】更新圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190409/large/1554808777_a64b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190409%2Flarge%2F1554808777_a64b.jpg&h=eef2eb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青衣發生刑毀案，下午4時許，長青邨有街坊報案，指一名手執枴杖的75歲老婦持菜刀狂劈商場平台一部滙豐櫃員機。警員接報到場，發現櫃員機螢幕玻璃爆裂，碎片散滿地上。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，拘捕該名老婦，涉嫌刑毀，她報稱手指受傷，由救護車送院治理。警方在現場撿獲一架超市手推車、一把30厘米長菜刀及一枝柺杖，相信是被捕老婦遺下的。警方正調查老婦破壞櫃員機的原因，案件交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第5隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/23/300eed1189fd640d2bd75a9843141gb5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F23%2F300eed1189fd640d2bd75a9843141gb5.JPG&h=adc89f2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa8d78b7a115f89e4f21eb446d8232933f6aee5e","tid":1099542,"uid":76563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T00:44:16.000Z","msg":"記錯密碼食卡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4185ad2212bfc143fbf37d67de97c1161cafb71","tid":1099542,"uid":17776,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T00:59:56.000Z","msg":"睇錯狂劈滙豐職員"},{"pid":"e46f9bc725dde5771c84e64c9218a81b5693b8c6","tid":1099542,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:04:11.000Z","msg":"入面開工個件點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03db56990a73b6d62e253e647c37348b08433d92","tid":1099542,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e46f9bc725dde5771c84e64c9218a81b5693b8c6","tid":1099542,"uid":25424,"lik